{"tid":51102,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"女人最鐘意就係你最忙既時候先搵你","createTime":"2016-12-23T02:58:21.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-24T12:25:55.000Z","uid":17677,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ab6409977b6d816ab14a582a6ec33fbcbfbbfa6e","tid":51102,"uid":17677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T02:58:21.000Z","msg":"咁前日一直都相安無事 <br />\n去到夜晚9點幾我老婆係我打緊ps4個陣先話有緊要野要傾(對佢黎講緊要) <br />\n咁我就膚顯佢幾句 佢見我鳩答就熄鳩部電視 我當堂呆左 我玩緊watch dog2 過埋小小就爆 我已經嬲嬲地<br />\n之後佢就繼續講  <br />\n<br />\n我心諗 你都痴撚線 <br />\n食飯個陣唔講 拖地個陣唔講 <br />\n係要9點幾10點我打機個陣講 <br />\n仲要講埋d垃圾 我已經無心機答佢 hea佢幾句就算<br />\n<br />\n去到琴晚我返到屋企食完飯諗住打機<br />\n但無啦啦開唔撚到機<br />\n之後我以為壞左睇左咩事 <br />\n我屌你老母無撚左條電線<br />\n之後我問我老婆點解唔見左條電線<br />\n我老婆話我成日打機唔理佢 佢收撚埋左<br />\n罰鳩我聖誕節唔撚俾打機<br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母你真係惡毒<br />\n唯一娛樂都無撚埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"def36fab580c575d93f239edd2c645aea7596c7d","tid":51102,"uid":33601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T02:59:09.000Z","msg":"有沒買糖水？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2adcc8037d7a5667f3f89aea5ec2cce8cb033552","tid":51102,"uid":60529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T02:59:37.000Z","msg":"打老婆巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"490067730de4ce986d1861d68e068d6da66e4daf","tid":51102,"uid":17677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T02:59:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有沒買糖水？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無呀！叫佢食屎啦"},{"pid":"48eb51708a5731a42f843029ca19bc852ec0d861","tid":51102,"uid":25359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T03:01:10.000Z","msg":"買糖水哄條八婆啦老婆奴<img src=\